### How to install?
Copy the dir to c:/ oder d:/. It is not working under c:/programm-files

### Prepation for using?
You should be sure, that port 80 is not in use

### How I start the service?
Click on the file start.bat. To quit on stop.bat

### Which Buttons are available?
F1-F12, a-z, 0-9, alt, shift, ctrl, del, enter, up, down, left, right

### Are combinations possible?
Yes, you have to change the value of the button in: space§a or alt§2

### How much is the delay?
<= 1 second

### Why is the delay so long?
The delay comes together for several reasons. Partly it is due to the Wlan and partly an HTML request is data intensive. Furthermore, there are currently several levels (HTML-Ajax/PHP/Python3). I try to minimize the time soon and remove the PHP part.

### Is it possible to find out the key-status in SC?
No, StarCitizen does not currently offer an API.

### Can it be used for other games?
All games and software products which work with hotkeys are possible.

### What are the limits of the surface?
You can design anything with HTML/Javascipt.

